479
00:31:10,880 --> 00:31:13,280
You should have come to see me before this, Mrs Evans.

480
00:31:13,280 --> 00:31:14,720
Nothing wrong, is there?

481
00:31:14,720 --> 00:31:17,160
No, but you're not exactly robust.

482
00:31:17,160 --> 00:31:20,040
I had the flu last year, but nothing since.

483
00:31:20,040 --> 00:31:21,960
And you're over 40, aren't you?

484
00:31:21,960 --> 00:31:23,360
Only just.

485
00:31:23,360 --> 00:31:26,720
Well, we needn't make any decision yet.

486
00:31:26,720 --> 00:31:28,160
Decision?

487
00:31:28,160 --> 00:31:31,080
I may have to suggest an operation.

488
00:31:32,960 --> 00:31:35,360
I see.

489
00:31:35,360 --> 00:31:37,080
Thank you, Doctor.

490
00:31:37,080 --> 00:31:38,920
I was at Finn's the night before last.

491
00:31:38,920 --> 00:31:40,160
Miracle none of us copped it.

492
00:31:40,160 --> 00:31:42,080
The guvnor was just standing around.

493
00:31:42,080 --> 00:31:44,960
This one's on the house, he said. And lummy, it was.

494
00:31:44,960 --> 00:31:47,400
- Well, dear? 
- Everything's all right.

495
00:31:47,400 --> 00:31:50,520
Waste of time and money it was, making me come and see the doctor.

496
00:31:50,520 --> 00:31:52,640
Your dad wanted to make quite sure, you know.

497
00:31:52,640 --> 00:31:54,080
Yes, of course.

498
00:31:54,080 --> 00:31:56,520
I always felt I'd failed him,

499
00:31:56,520 --> 00:31:58,440
but never a word of reproach.

500
00:31:58,440 --> 00:32:00,800
There's kind he is, all through.

501
00:32:00,800 --> 00:32:03,840
But now, now I won't fail him.

502
00:32:03,840 --> 00:32:05,960
- I know I won't. 
- Of course you won't, dear.

